</h2>
<p>This meta-EIP specifies the changes included in the Ethereum hardfork named Istanbul.</p>
<h2 id="specification">
<a href="#specification" class="anchor-link"></a> Specification
</h2>
<ul>
<li>Codename: Istanbul</li>
