<h3 id="included-eips">
<a href="#included-eips" class="anchor-link"></a> Included EIPs
</h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="/EIPS/eip-152">EIP-152</a>: Add Blake2 compression function <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">F</code> precompile</li>
